note right of src_utils_workspaceFs : Manages file system operations for architecture and UML artifacts.
note right of src_utils_plantUml : Processes and validates PlantUML diagrams.
note right of src_utils_governance : Synchronizes governance reports between intent and implementation UML.
note right of src_utils_git : Interacts with Git to retrieve commit and file change information.
note right of src_utils_agentHandoff : Builds prompts for agent handoff workflows.
note right of src_participant : Handles chat requests and responses for the participant system.
note right of src_lm_prompts : Generates prompts for various user and system interactions.
note right of src_lm_chatModelHelper : Manages interactions with the language model chat system.
note right of src_extension : Handles activation and deactivation of the VS Code extension.
note right of StitchJudge : Analyzes architecture drift and performs anti-corruption checks.
note right of SemanticUmlEngine : Abstract engine for semantic analysis and UML generation.
note right of src_engine_lspCollector : Collects and processes source code symbols and topology.
note right of DefaultSemanticUmlEngine : Implements semantic analysis and UML generation with specific strategies.
note right of src_commands_link : Handles linking operations in the chat system.
note right of src_commands_init : Handles initialization operations in the chat system.
note right of src_commands_evolve : Handles an evolve command with no external dependencies.
note right of src_commands_discover : Processes a discover command and cleans PlantUML strings.
note right of src_commands_baseline : Handles a baseline command and resolves target URIs while analyzing call graphs.


